-1.entity_name: workers on the construction of the pyramids
-1.entity_description: Laborers building the pyramids who reportedly organized an early strike.
-1.resolution_context: One of the earliest recorded protests in history dates back to ancient Egypt, where workers on the construction of the pyramids reportedly staged a strike to demand better working conditions and wages.
